ncia clara de que los aneurismas disecantes aumenten el riesgo de ACV recurrente.","guid":"IYj4w1FK228d84qnJjYwjg","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"260","text":"🔹 Tasa de nueva disección:","guid":"GAS70WENaxIoFdRpBazchA","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"✅ 2% a los 3 meses (CADISP).","guid":"XqKKhh639aQp94OVHXVBrQ","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"✅ 16% al año en algunos estudios (mayoría dentro del primer mes).","guid":"NW3EYgBdhQ1BfTWjJ1rKfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"260","text":"🔹 Factores de riesgo\\Npara nueva disección:","guid":"dMt2MTyWGklbNJATGGStWw","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"✔️ Edad joven.","guid":"QvGR1Qr20atrhA2MTci4XA","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"✔️ Historia familiar de DAC.","guid":"Y0AsYWYFLAUEDbYAdgCXaA","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"✔️ Ehlers-Danlos vascular o displasia fibromuscular.","guid":"PLO55l0V60EKP8QFXjyyqQ","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"269","text":"✔️ Antecedentes de múltiples disecciones.","guid":"LmDGsCgzTqwEcuM4RmWCgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"260","text":"🔹 Se recomienda evitar traumatismos cervicales (ej. deportes de contacto, manipulación quiropráctica).","guid":"CUC5viyIt6FMEl8GZ-NERA","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"250","text":"3️⃣ Pronóstico Funcional","guid":"S0CtRXYJ4psFWIXyAK5xqA","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"🔹 Buen pronóstico funcional en 75-82% de los casos (mRS 0-1).","guid":"dmdnqEbVu5UoCTwlazLd2Q","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"🔹 Mortalidad <5%.","guid":"A2vV3wM9zDgDl4s0Rl1ntA","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"🔹 Predictores de buen pronóstico:","guid":"DjSd5G8bmMAUJiARcXTKRQ","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"✅ Bajo NIHSS inicial.","guid":"VSDExRgz1hFndWGuEdR-qw","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"278","text":"✅ Edad joven.","guid":"dUnBUnG1JbNwETFVI6qIAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"275","text":"🔹 Factores de peor pronóstico:","guid":"Geh0X3SEFI1qEAqEIykuHQ","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"❌ Disección carotídea.","guid":"IQzMLjYiaYoLDHJhbE15dA","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"281","text":"❌ Oclusión arterial.","guid":"LCxMJRBk-FNs--scIpOzzQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"275","text":"🔹 Secuelas comunes:","guid":"Vzqz6RUFJ0ENxpGnWqaJyA","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"✅ 40% reportan afectación en calidad de vida a 6 meses.","guid":"GELzehFeHNshA_F8JneRXg","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"284","text":"✅ Cefalea persistente en algunos pacientes.","guid":"AHm1nDUqEY0X7FujVZp6YQ","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"284","text":"✅ Posible desarrollo de síndrome de estrés postraumático.","guid":"TV3nn39hvVFnbvkNQqeo8Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"288","parent":"0","text":"ENSAYOS CLÍNICOS SOBRE\\NTRATAMIENTO EN DISECCIÓN\\NDE ARTERIA CERVICAL","guid":"T6WgrjHRbmo-HyiVe7D_7Q","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"1️⃣ CADISS (Cervical Artery\\NDissection in Stroke Study)","guid":"SbzALgvfAfEY5oXzc16cfw","children":[{"id":"290","parent":"289","text":"🔹 Objetivo: Comparar antiagregación vs. anticoagulación en la prevención del ACV recurrente en disección de arteria cervical.","guid":"N2QmrGMt24Bf6-d3Kp0LYg","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"289","text":"🔹 Diseño: Ensayo multicéntrico, abierto, aleatorizado.","guid":"TEYn4WUp_x9KfI66a7Pkbw","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"289","text":"🔹 Población:","guid":"KQqOQFfAWqpbqVddft3qEA","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"✔️ 250 pacientes con disección extracraneal (187 carotídea, 53 vertebral).","guid":"U_iTfgnGGRF6W4DMMSQPQg","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"292","text":"✔️ 90% con ACV o AIT.","guid":"XzfqtlzRk78h6j5yJ5v4dA","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"292","text":"✔️ Tratamiento con antiplaquetarios o anticoagulantes decidido por el médico tratante.","guid":"UqHuDTeqlRt7-BJnVQFdyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"296","parent":"289","text":"🔹 Seguimiento: 3 meses y 1 año.","guid":"EwyIeVXi6UBDmgg-XMlIqA","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"289","text":"🔹 Resultados:","guid":"YcHrMVyAjjJQJ-UnGSYR3Q","children":[{"id":"298","parent":"297","text":"✅ No hubo diferencia significativa en ACV recurrente entre ambos grupos.","guid":"P65psjATzJ5Dwx0_C_SRkw","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"297","text":"✅ Tasa de ACV a 3 meses: 2% en anticoagulación vs. 3% en antiagregación.","guid":"FT3LvQ4_q_l3qHYCPkhZ_Q","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"297","text":"✅ No hubo diferencias en recanalización vascular.","guid":"ZgAGpFNRzV89JkQNOfiaIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"301","parent":"289","text":"🔹 Limitaciones:","guid":"XRfmcTeBxNlrHKllPE_RJw","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"❌ Muestra pequeña con pocos eventos de ACV recurrente.","guid":"FFNYmA0G59dj68mbZvVGpg","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"301","text":"❌ Falta de confirmación por imágenes en 20% de los casos.","guid":"RLF88l_j3AI79qRuV74FbA","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"301","text":"❌ Heterogeneidad en el uso de antiagregantes.","guid":"NcbFQn-QrK00h04UF4iwcw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"305","parent":"288","text":"2️⃣ TREAT-CAD (Biomarkers and Antithrombotic\\NTreatment in Cervical Artery Dissection)","guid":"XBE63wSvMzswrsJRG7-kkQ","children":[{"id":"306","parent":"305","text":"🔹 Objetivo: Evaluar si aspirina no es inferior a antagonistas de vitamina K en la prevención del ACV en DAC.","guid":"NML_2XRx35AntDYlSgDLlg","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"305","text":"🔹 Diseño: Ensayo multicéntrico, abierto, aleatorizado, de no inferioridad.","guid":"ArGLih9crCcISSWUaLGSLg","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"305","text":"🔹 Población:","guid":"cq55h0VvaaEiqixQT8Zf-A","children":[{"id":"309","parent":"308","text":"✔️ 194 pacientes con disección extracraneal sintomática confirmada por RM.","guid":"fPEuew3G1bUMFjEfEUSHEw","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"308","text":"✔️ Tratamiento con aspirina 300 mg/día vs. anticoagulación con antagonistas de vitamina K.","guid":"Gs29jXAB-rt4Oc25X386fw","children":[]}]},{"id":"311","parent":"305","text":"🔹 Seguimiento: 3 meses.","guid":"T-XWvTQwcig3PT_rBaycAA","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"305","text":"🔹 Resultados:","guid":"M8Ee1WvEjf8dNUxzD9JZtA","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"❌ Aspirina NO cumplió con el criterio de no inferioridad frente a la anticoagulación.","guid":"cHPBOk3kDsQrkf5FJTbBEw","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"312","text":"✅ ACV en 7 pacientes del grupo aspirina vs. 0 en anticoagulación.","guid":"QlXuVVNGNGpvN4yqRQd53w","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"312","text":"✅ Mayoría de ACV ocurrieron en los primeros 7 días de tratamiento.","guid":"cqLgkneAsj4tuQwNZVFaGQ","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"312","text":"✅ No hubo diferencia en hemorragia intracraneal o muerte.","guid":"PPAb31BjOF01F7oROeFKWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"317","parent":"305","text":"🔹 Limitaciones:","guid":"XioOE0Et6zBLJdFuePfLoA","children":[{"id":"318","parent":"317","text":"❌ Tiempo a la aleatorización variable, pudiendo perder eventos tempranos.","guid":"MS_l60NfnydYdwYfARW8qQ","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"317","text":"❌ Falta de poder estadístico para diferenciar claramente entre tratamientos.","guid":"d5ARTw-0RgsGwlipK1EwJA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"288","text":"CONCLUSIÓN\\NCLÍNICA","guid":"d9uVQCbyKCIR7_czNMuxIA","children":[{"id":"321","parent":"320","text":"📌 Ambos estudios sugieren que anticoagulación y antiagregación tienen tasas similares de ACV recurrente en DAC.","guid":"e3jUCiP3pRw7I4nYa-yVRQ","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"320","text":"📌 TREAT-CAD no confirmó la no inferioridad de aspirina, lo que sugiere que anticoagulación puede ser preferida en los primeros días, sobre todo en casos con trombo intraluminal.","guid":"cduz4Wa1iB4RI1ZYNDGiNg","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"320","text":"📌 Decisión individualizada según características del paciente (gravedad de la disección, trombosis intraluminal, riesgo hemorrágico).","guid":"Ofu8iABa4wJ5ORwVLJ6dGg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"324","parent":"0","text":"RESUMEN","guid":"SZnwNUZab61VRKT2INSkHg","children":[{"id":"325","parent":"324","text":"1️⃣ Importancia Clínica","guid":"W1-W72MLNp17ey3mc6KKaQ","children":[{"id":"326","parent":"325","text":"✔️ Causa importante de ACV en adultos jóvenes.","guid":"dGlTeRx_H2MaGhvHdOMJFQ","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"325","text":"✔️ Su detección temprana permite tratamiento precoz con agentes antitrombóticos, reduciendo riesgo de eventos isquémicos.","guid":"Uakw8DIGd2pKfYN2HwcYjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"328","parent":"324","text":"2️⃣ Fisiopatología","guid":"MWg0vDHsfINhrsGBIn8XwA","children":[{"id":"329","parent":"328","text":"✔️ Separación de capas arteriales → falsa luz → entrada de sangre → formación de hematoma intramural.","guid":"CWym5UgA8nUtfm8kVXDl1A","children":[]},{"id":"330","parent":"328","text":"✔️ Puede generar estenosis, oclusión arterial o aneurismas disecantes.","guid":"GGMt7lum9KRCgfDyHufS8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"331","parent":"324","text":"3️⃣ Factores de Riesgo","guid":"FNvshhvgdYNRmMQbXnXcvA","children":[{"id":"332","parent":"331","text":"✔️ Genéticos:","guid":"YjrlMSbdaRF_SoDaPZp8IA","children":[{"id":"333","parent":"332","text":"✅ Ehlers-Danlos vascular (2% de los casos).","guid":"Ceifr3rFrsExPQaJflHzKA","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"332","text":"✅ Displasia fibromuscular.","guid":"F0TOJEtXIlBzNPw9aO3_FA","children":[]}]},{"id":"335","parent":"331","text":"✔️ Ambientales:","guid":"fV2Zuj2yf7MH9RekLsXOdg","children":[{"id":"336","parent":"335","text":"✅ Trauma menor (hiperextensión cervical, rotación, tos fuerte, manipulación quiropráctica).","guid":"b578N2mj2SVRROY3eQujHA","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"335","text":"✅ Embarazo y postparto.","guid":"MaTLmn7DVVtOfIjxSgf5iQ","children":[]},{"id":"338","parent":"335","text":"✅ Migraña.","guid":"WmpJ_xD-eeNo78x7b0Y2hg","children":[]},{"id":"339","parent":"335","text":"✅ Uso de anticonceptivos orales.","guid":"LN7vZjqIkJZNvBNCDxnUlw","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"335","text":"✅ Infecciones recientes.","guid":"YWX5p00GlBxMtFC3a06ZVg","children":[]},{"id":"341","parent":"335","text":"✅ Factores de riesgo vascular (hipertensión, tabaquismo).","guid":"R8xC3X3xV0BpoIx-XxERAQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"342","parent":"324","text":"4️⃣ Presentación Clínica","guid":"SUh5kFzViLtH_xAWRqYTSw","children":[{"id":"343","parent":"342","text":"✔️ Síntomas locales (57-69%):","guid":"GogIb0_0J7p1a-HBCicEpg","children":[{"id":"344","parent":"343","text":"✅ Cefalea (anterior en DAC de carótida, occipital en DAC de vertebral).","guid":"OZgA30awx_gDMqfCazzMeQ","children":[]},{"id":"345","parent":"343","text":"✅ Dolor cervical.","guid":"RXQdU1GvMLM1RMYCH95nUw","children":[]},{"id":"346","parent":"343","text":"✅ Horner parcial (ptosis + miosis sin anhidrosis).","guid":"Yq2qlh40kn0PJJ3ZD4yZ_Q","children":[]},{"id":"347","parent":"343","text":"✅ Tinnitus pulsátil.","guid":"WL0jE1zgsRsepm6UOiMcuw","children":[]}]},{"id":"348","parent":"342","text":"✔️ Síntomas neurológicos:","guid":"KedFN2tav0wlcbYRcbOIFQ","children":[{"id":"349","parent":"348","text":"✅ ACV por embolismo arteria-arteria (67% de los casos).","guid":"aUwWjA8SQpBQxJkWMpSQHQ","children":[]},{"id":"350","parent":"348","text":"✅ Isquemia por hipoperfusión distal (menos frecuente).","guid":"a-fLSxjDqSx5OqNoBm_Tug","children":[]},{"id":"351","parent":"348","text":"✅ Hemorragia subaracnoidea en disecciones intracraneales (1%).","guid":"aLfQ5m6mhSkQlthgIk_RxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"352","parent":"342","text":"✔️ Tiempo de progresión:","guid":"NVdNIhPJgCMNjJ4_estqdQ","children":[{"id":"353","parent":"352","text":"✅ Síntomas locales pueden preceder el ACV por horas a semanas.","guid":"ZXiw1kLRZEEaqdHISCZbbQ","children":[]},{"id":"354","parent":"352","text":"✅ Mayor riesgo de ACV en los primeros 7-14 días tras síntomas locales.","guid":"YQX2vynOb6FXsvVqOcMZ0g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"355","parent":"324","text":"5️⃣ Diagnóstico","guid":"Bq8gvHZZY_5z5jaNMJZl9A","children":[{"id":"356","parent":"355","text":"✔️ Sospecha clínica\\Nen pacientes con:","guid":"YbQjShlX7J8iSe4JSwA51w","children":[{"id":"357","parent":"356","text":"✅ Horner + cefalea + ACV ipsilateral.","guid":"KGovL3MOhx99lMn0FFH6eg","children":[]},{"id":"358","parent":"356","text":"✅ Historia de trauma menor o factores predisponentes.","guid":"C9IwTHbPbVwawc41dIoBMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"359","parent":"355","text":"✔️ Neuroimagen:","guid":"ZXXyhStYppUW2dL4Gs0_pw","children":[{"id":"360","parent":"359","text":"✅ MRA o CTA:","guid":"PyImuCRmcTcVmKodJJrXjw","children":[{"id":"361","parent":"360","text":"• Estenosis cónica larga.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"362","parent":"360","text":"• Oclusión “en llama”.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"363","parent":"360","text":"• Aneurisma disecante.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"364","parent":"360","text":"• Signo de la media luna (hematoma intramural en T1 con supresión de grasa).","guid":"VjF3e0efJqtyrDmTFx32Zw","children":[]}]},{"id":"365","parent":"359","text":"✅ DSA solo si alta sospecha con imágenes no concluyentes.","guid":"ZzfVeDBCe-VswTL8SD3MNw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"366","parent":"324","text":"6️⃣ Tratamiento","guid":"WhDrh0R0KGYCAOYKYMAMQw","children":[{"id":"367","parent":"366","text":"✔️ Tratamiento del ACV agudo:","guid":"Os2MZHXnHJcRVnI3HIGvrw","children":[{"id":"368","parent":"367","text":"✅ Trombólisis IV si no contraindicado.","guid":"Dz8JNjOgYEBngemGN6k4ZQ","children":[]},{"id":"369","parent":"367","text":"✅ Trombectomía mecánica en oclusión de gran vaso.","guid":"Jq7nYGUWs3pL-zLgMoEXrA","children":[]},{"id":"370","parent":"367","text":"✅ Stenting carotídeo en oclusiones severas post-reperfusión.","guid":"W-Yg1ma9ARUnCxjeQVwTWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"371","parent":"366","text":"✔️ Prevención secundaria\\N(AHA/ASA 2021):","guid":"EhWnqj3k69ZcKVMDUTfOYw","children":[{"id":"372","parent":"371","text":"✅ Aspirina o Warfarina (sin superioridad comprobada).","guid":"YktdDXHB_SB10qXySYMyhg","children":[]},{"id":"373","parent":"371","text":"✅ Riesgo de ACV recurrente bajo tras tratamiento.","guid":"IgR5BWKT2O4RwP69fBVkjA","children":[]},{"id":"374","parent":"371","text":"✅ Terapia ≥3 meses, luego evaluar continuación con imágenes.","guid":"JwgBVBPB5Mdc1XDQYdWNuA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"375","parent":"324","text":"7️⃣ Pronóstico","guid":"CakBX24r4wd-Vz1nGOgKlQ","children":[{"id":"376","parent":"375","text":"✔️ Recanalización:","guid":"A0l28CIHWzJoMg6ZFV8emg","children":[{"id":"377","parent":"376","text":"✅ Carótida: 16% (1 mes), 50% (3 meses), 60% (6-12 meses).","guid":"IcxDSGXZJu1QkUL7SHsqqA","children":[]},{"id":"378","parent":"376","text":"✅ Vertebral: evolución similar.","guid":"Su_aZxyMddt6_EJUJtX7PQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"379","parent":"375","text":"✔️ Riesgo de ACV recurrente:","guid":"Pv1r3R171VpUNzxOZgVtMQ","children":[{"id":"380","parent":"379","text":"✅ 2-4% a los 3 meses, 2.5% al año.","guid":"X-xHCURbYZxmluz9QjekFg","children":[]},{"id":"381","parent":"379","text":"✅ Mayor riesgo en primeras 2 semanas.","guid":"Nh1evFxpku8LutacWCHXwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"382","parent":"375","text":"✔️ Recurrente DAC:","guid":"HziQJUYyOFFTzsYWQQTTbQ","children":[{"id":"383","parent":"382","text":"✅ 2% a los 3 meses, hasta 16% al año (mayoría en el primer mes).","guid":"MT26ITEMrR5H2vrqOua7gA","children":[]}]},{"id":"384","parent":"375","text":"✔️ Mortalidad baja (<5%).","guid":"LAtfPyRgCREJf_4Vdvs5pg","children":[]},{"id":"385","parent":"375","text":"✔️ Secuelas\\Nposibles:","guid":"QOx-7AR8QGkd0TTkRDX13A","children":[{"id":"386","parent":"385","text":"✅ Cefalea persistente en algunos pacientes.","guid":"JoObnAYDQ31ZlRR2Bm_ipQ","children":[]},{"id":"387","parent":"385","text":"✅ Impacto en calidad de vida (40% a 6 meses).","guid":"Sl6lGUAsAXRIp4a7AHwD1Q","children":[]},{"id":"388","parent":"385","text":"✅ Posible estrés postraumático tras el evento.","guid":"HJWUY1RiXVhYnduWW5MAQQ","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":388,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Neurología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Continuum. Disección de Arterias Cervicales (DAC)-2025","id":"map_1394","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Continuum. Disección de Arterias Cervicales (DAC)-2025"}